author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Mexico Records 7th Coronavirus Death — 475 Confirmed Cases
description: A Mexican governor announced that a patient in his state has died, marking the seventh fatality for the novel Coronavirus (Covid-19) in the country. Officials most recently confirmed a total of 475 cases nationwide.
